@startuml DeviceStatusManager_Sequence_GetStatus

title UML Диаграмма последовательностей: Запрос статуса устройства через API

actor "API Gateway" as API
participant "APIController" as Controller
participant "DeviceStatusManager" as DSM
participant "IDeviceRepository" as Repository
participant "DeviceStatus" as Status
participant "DeviceStatusDto" as DTO

API -> Controller: GET /api/v1/devices/{id}/status
activate Controller

Controller -> DSM: getStatus(deviceId)
activate DSM

DSM -> Repository: findById(deviceId)
activate Repository

Repository --> DSM: Optional<Device>
deactivate Repository

alt Устройство найдено
  DSM -> Status: isOnline()
  activate Status
  Status --> DSM: boolean
  deactivate Status

  DSM -> DTO: new DeviceStatusDto(device, isOnline)
  activate DTO
  DTO --> DSM: statusDto
  deactivate DTO

  DSM --> Controller: DeviceStatusDto
else Устройство не найдено
  DSM --> Controller: 404 Not Found
end

deactivate DSM

Controller --> API: 200 OK + JSON
deactivate Controller

@enduml